DarkMouse::

She smirked and went back to the console.  She sat down and started 
studying the scematics for the ship.  She learned the lay out of the 
ship and where she could get her hands on some weapons if she needed 
them in a hurry.  She smiled and looked back over her shoulder at 
Galvatron. "Want some energon to help wake you up?"  She got up and 
went to the mess hall.  She came back a few minutes later with a cup 
of liquid energon for Galvatron. She left it on the side of the desk 
for him and went back to her console and studying the prints for the 
ship.
